<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>TASK MASTER â€” Aktivasi Akun</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f3f6fb;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 10px;
        background-color: #f3f6fb;
      }

      .card {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 14px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c853, #64dd17);
        padding: 28px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 28px;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .info-box {
        background-color: #f9fafc;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #ececec;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 18px 0;
      }

      .info-item {
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .info-item strong {
        color: #111;
      }

      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }

      .cta-button {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c853, #64dd17);
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 15px;
        display: inline-block;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.4);
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #666;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
          padding: 12px 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }

        .greeting {
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="header">
          <div class="logo">TASK MASTER</div>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.9">
            Aktivasi Akun
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <p class="greeting">Halo <%= first_name %>,</p>

          <p>
            Terima kasih sudah bergabung dengan <strong>TASK MASTER</strong>.
            Untuk mulai menggunakan akun kamu, silakan lakukan aktivasi terlebih
            dahulu melalui tombol di bawah ini.
          </p>

          <div class="info-box">
            <div class="info-item">
              <strong>Nama:</strong> <%= first_name %> <%= last_name %>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item"><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></div>
            <div class="info-item">
              <strong>Tanggal Daftar:</strong> <%= createdAt %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-wrapper">
            <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="cta-button">
              ðŸš€ Aktifkan Akun
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="note">
            Jika tombol di atas tidak bekerja, copy & paste link berikut ke
            browser kamu:
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 12px; word-break: break-all">
            <%= activationLink %>
          </p>

          <p class="note">
            Apabila kamu tidak merasa mendaftar di TASK MASTER, silakan abaikan
            email ini.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 TASK MASTER â€” All rights reserved</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
